  Sorcerer spells::section.class_spell_list
    0th-level Sorcerer spells::table.spell_list
      ::head
        |
      ::row
        [Acid Splash]      | Orb deals 1d3 acid damage.
        [Dancing Lights]   | Creates torches or other lights.
        [Daze]             | Humanoid creature of 4 HD or less loses next action.
        [Detect Magic]     | Detects spells and magic items within 60 ft.
        [Disrupt Undead]   | Deals 1d6 damage to one undead.
        [Electric Jolt]    | Ranged Touch attack deals 1d3 electricity damage.
        [Flare]            | Dazzles one creature (-1 on attack rolls).
        [Ghost Sound]      | Figment sounds.
        [Light]            | Object shines like a torch.
        [Mage Hand]        | 5-pound telekinesis.
        [Open/Close]       | Opens or closes small or light things.
        [Prestidigitation] | Performs minor tricks.
        [Ray of Frost]     | Ray deals 1d3 cold damage.
        [Reload]           | reloads one mustket/pistol/crossbow per level.
        [Sonic Snap]       | Subject saves or takes 1 point of sonic damage is deaf for 1 round.
        [Stick]            | Glues an object weighing 5 pounds or less to another object.
    1st-level Sorcerer spells::table.spell_list
      ::head
        |
      ::row
        [Animate Rope]                        | Makes a rope move at your command.
        [Benign Transposition]                | Two willing subjects swap places.
        [Betrayal of Flesh]                   | Subjects flesh starts to rot away, dealing 1d6 damage per round
        [Burning Hands]                       | 1d4/level fire damage (max 5d4).
        [Cause Fear]                          | One creature of 5 HD or less flees for 1d4 rounds.
        [Charm Person]                        | Makes one person your friend.
        [Color Spray]                         | Knocks unconscious, blinds, and/or stuns weak creatures.
        [Corrosive Grasp]                     | 1 touch/level deals 1d8 acid damage.
        [Detect Secret Doors]                 | Reveals hidden doors within 60 ft.
        [Disguise Self]                       | Changes your appearance.
        [Enwebben]                            | Shoot a web at someone.
        [Expeditious Retreat]                 | You and your allies run away.
        [Feather Fall]                        | Objects or creatures fall slowly.
        [Floating Disk]                       | Creates 3-ft.-diameter horizontal disk that holds 20 slots./level.
        [Grease]                              | Makes 10-ft. square or one object slippery.
        [Hypnotism]                           | Hypnotize 1d6 creatures.
        [Identify]                            | Determines properties of magic item.
        [Jump]                                | Subject gets bonus on Jump checks.
        [Lesser Elemental Orb]                | Orb of cold (water), fire (fire), bludgeoning (earth), or slashing (wind) deals 1d8 + 1d8/2 levels damage. Ranged Touch attack.
        [Mage Armor]                          | Gives subject +4 armor bonus.
        [Magic Missile]                       | 1d4+1 damage; +1 missile per two levels above 1st (max 5).
        [Magic Weapon]                        | Weapon gains +1 bonus.
        [Obscuring Mist]                      | Fog surrounds you.
        [Protection from Chaos/Evil/Good/Law] | +2 to AC and saves, counter mind control.
        [Shield]                              | Invisible disc gives +2/+4 shield bonus to AC, blocks magic missiles.
        [Shocking Grasp]                      | Touch delivers 1d6/level electricity damage (max 5d6).
        [Silent Image]                        | Creates minor illusion of your design.
        [Sleep]                               | Puts 4 HD of creatures into magical slumber.
        [Unseen Servant]                      | Invisible force obeys your commands.
    2nd-level Sorcerer spells::table.spell_list
      ::head
        |
      ::row
        [Acid Arrow]             | Ranged touch attack; 2d4 damage for 1 round +1 round/three levels.
        [Baleful Transposition]  | Two unwilling targets swap positions.
        [Blindness/Deafness]     | Makes subject blinded or deafened.
        [Blur]                   | Attacks miss subject 20% of the time.
        [Combust]                | Subject takes 1d8/level fire damage and might catch fire.
        [Darkness]               | 20-ft. radius of supernatural shadow.
        [Daze Monster]           | Living creature of 6 HD or less loses next action.
        [Electric Loop]          | Deals 1d6/level electricity damage plus stunning to a single creature.
        [False Life]             | Gain 1d10 temporary hp +1/level (max +10).
        [Flaming Sphere]         | Creates rolling ball of fire, 2d6 damage, lasts 1 round/level.
        [Fog Cloud]              | Fog obscures vision.
        [Ghoul Touch]            | Paralyzes one subject, which exudes stench that makes those nearby sickened.
        [Gust of Wind]           | Blows away or knocks down smaller creatures for 1rd/level.
        [Hideous Laughter]       | Subject loses actions for 1 round/level.
        [Hypnotic Pattern]       | Fascinates (2d4 + level) HD of creatures.
        [Invisibility]           | Subject is invisible for 1 min./level or until it attacks.
        [Knock]                  | Opens locked or magically sealed door.
        [Mirror Image]           | Creates decoy duplicates of you (1d4 +1 per three levels, max 8).
        [Protection from Arrows] | Subject gains DR 10 to most ranged attacks.
        [Pyrotechnics]           | Turns fire into blinding light or choking smoke.
        [Resist Energy]          | Ignores 10 (or more) points of damage/attack from specified energy type.
        [Scare]                  | Frightens creatures of less than 6 HD.
        [Scorching Ray]          | Ranged touch attack deals 1d6/level fire damage.
        [See Invisibility]       | Reveals invisible creatures or objects.
        [Shatter]                | Sonic vibration damages objects or crystalline creatures.
        [Snowball Swarm]         | Snowballs deal 2d6 points of cold damage in 10' burst.
        [Web]                    | Fills 20-ft.-radius spread with sticky spiderwebs.
    3rd-level Sorcerer spells::table.spell_list
      ::head
        |
      ::row
        [Chain Missiles]                                 | 1 magic missile per two levels strike one target, then one fewer another, then one fewer another, etc.
        [Daylight]                                       | 60-ft. radius of bright light.
        [Deep Slumber]                                   | Puts 10 HD of creatures to sleep.
        [Dispel Magic]                                   | Cancels magical spells and effects.
        [Displacement]                                   | Attacks miss subject 50%.
        [Fireball]                                       | 1d6 damage per level, 20-ft. radius.
        [Flame Arrow]                                    | Shoot fiery arrows at people.
        [Fly]                                            | Subject flies at speed of 60 ft.
        [Haste]                                          | One creature/level moves faster, +1 on attack rolls, AC, and Reflex saves.
        [Hold Person]                                    | Paralyzes one humanoid for 1 round/level.
        [Invisibility 10' radius]                        | Makes everyone within 10 ft. invisible.
        [Lightning Bolt]                                 | Electricity deals 1d6/level damage.
        [Mass Mage Armor]                                | one creature per level gains mage armor.
        [Mass Shield]                                    | one creature per level gains shield.
        [Major Image]                                    | As silent image, plus sound, smell and thermal effects.
        [Protection from Chaos/Evil/Good/Law 10' Radius] | As protection spells, but 10-ft. radius and 10 min./level.
        [Reverse Arrows]                                 | Like Protection From Arrows, but arrows reflect back.
        [Shrink Item]                                    | Object shrinks to one-sixteenth size.
        [Slow]                                           | Creatures are slowed
        [Suggestion]                                     | Compels subject to follow stated course of action.
        [Vampiric Touch]                                 | Touch deals 1d6/two levels damage; caster gains damage as hp.
        [Water Breathing]                                | Subject can breathe underwater.
        [Wind Gale]                                      | 30' cone deals 1d6 slashing damage per level.
